ATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 playable mages with different gameplay styles<br></li><li>40+ fantastic creatures to join or challenge your party<br></li><li>30+ artifacts, each one with 4 different rarities<br></li><li>Multiple offensive and defensive spells<br></li><li>20+ hand-designed, small locations with unique themes<br></li><li>A world that evolves between adventures - new locations, artifacts, and spells that open up more possibilities<br></li><li>Dynamic skirmishes happening in real-time without changing the game view for maximum immersion<br></li><li>Relatively short runs (about 1 hour)</li></ul><br>Add to the wishlist and follow to stay in touch!<br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ain't Nobody Got Time for That","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/052dff2f63af93031fb5b4021c0c97ed68391a7f.jpg"},{"name":"Buff Guy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/1796049500e418ab3a325fdc51bb6dab7c14c5de.jpg"},{"name":"Demanding Team","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/6fe659f0cd7bb0cd71c46f31d75bcd37fe35427a.jpg"},{"name":"Dragon Resistant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/55187f5f89a0a9c2d96d50b648e09700fe3f78e4.jpg"},{"name":"Leave No One Behind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/d8a94e54e17c8ac0475256f548347a2b8da1c96b.jpg"},{"name":"Look Mom No Units","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/dc83bc2b156ae245a58366bed515967fb97be6b1.jpg"},{"name":"Lord of Everything","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/e39b3b1028ae5623fd6b7df0830767b1a099058c.jpg"},{"name":"Perfect Fit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326050/e787485015172bb17ebbac229ff26398fd6557aa.jpg"},{"name":"Quick 